  <diagram id="roadmap" name="Perbaikan &amp; Penambahan">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1600" dy="900" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1600" pageHeight="900" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="r0"/>
        <mxCell id="r1" parent="r0"/>

        <mxCell id="r_title" value="SmartOrder Roadmap Teknis" style="text;html=1;fontSize=20;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="r1">
          <mxGeometry x="600" y="40" width="400" height="40" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="r_fix" value="Perbaikan Utama" style="swimlane;horizontal=0;childLayout=stackLayout;resizeParent=1;collapsible=0;" vertex="1" parent="r1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="120" width="650" height="620" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_add" value="Fitur yang Disarankan" style="swimlane;horizontal=0;childLayout=stackLayout;resizeParent=1;collapsible=0;" vertex="1" parent="r1">
          <mxGeometry x="840" y="120" width="650" height="620" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Fixes -->
        <mxCell id="r_fix_migration" value="1. Lengkapi Schema Diskon Warung&#10;- Tambah kolom: max_discount_percent, max_discount_amount, require_owner_auth_for_discount.&#10;- Pastikan sesuai dengan logika di OrderController@updateDiscount.&#10;- Tambah form di Owner/Admin untuk mengubah batas diskon." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_fix">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="60" width="610" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_fix_domain" value="2. Satukan Konfigurasi Domain/Subdomain&#10;- Buat helper tunggal untuk URL customer &amp; dashboard.&#10;- Gunakan SMARTORDER_DOMAIN dan app.url sebagai sumber utama.&#10;- Hilangkan hardcode smartorder.local:8080 dan smartorder.dev." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_fix">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="200" width="610" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_fix_reload" value="3. Kurangi Full Page Reload&#10;- Ganti location.reload() di dashboard &amp; customer status.&#10;- Manfaatkan SSE (streamStatus/streamOrders) atau AJAX partial refresh.&#10;- Prioritas: status customer, dashboard kasir, kitchen, waiter." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_fix">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="340" width="610" height="130" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_fix_wa" value="4. Perketat Validasi Nomor WhatsApp&#10;- Tambah rule: hanya digit, panjang 10–15 karakter.&#10;- Normalisasi ke format konsisten (mis. 628xx...).&#10;- Gunakan flag warung.whatsapp_notification untuk mengontrol pengiriman." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_fix">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="490" width="610" height="130" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

        <!-- Additions -->
        <mxCell id="r_add_dashboard_default" value="1. Tambah View dashboard.default&#10;- Ditampilkan jika role tidak dikenali atau belum punya dashboard khusus.&#10;- Berisi pesan jelas + tombol logout + info kontak admin." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_add">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="60" width="610" height="110" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_add_subscription" value="2. Enforce Subscription Warung&#10;- Jika subscription_expires_at lewat: tampilkan warning di dashboard owner.&#10;- Opsi: batasi order baru atau akses staff.&#10;- Logika sederhana dulu, bisa dikembangkan kemudian." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_add">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="190" width="610" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_add_health" value="3. Health Check &amp; Monitoring&#10;- Endpoint /health untuk cek DB &amp; env penting (FONNTE_TOKEN, SMARTORDER_DOMAIN).&#10;- Tambah log terstruktur untuk error WA &amp; sinkronisasi Google Sheets." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_add">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="330" width="610" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_add_services" value="4. Refactor Services ke Dependency Injection&#10;- Ubah NotificationService &amp; GoogleSheetService menjadi service non-static.&#10;- Inject ke controller agar mudah di-test dan diganti provider.&#10;- Siapkan ruang untuk provider WA lain / integrasi payment." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_add">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="470" width="610" height="130" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r_add_closing" value="5. Penguatan Flow Closing Kasir&#10;- Modal konfirmasi dengan ringkasan total_sales &amp; transaction_count.&#10;- Tombol export laporan closing harian dari layar kasir.&#10;- Sinkronisasi dengan laporan owner &amp; admin." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="r_add">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="620" width="610" height="120" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>

